---
---

<section class="exec-section exec-section-auto exec-reality" id="exec-reality">
  <div class="reality-bg">
    <img src="/branding-identity/backgrounds/gradient-simple.png" alt="" class="reality-bg-img" />
    <div class="reality-overlay"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="reality-content">
    <div class="exec-inner">
      <div class="exec-label">The Reality</div>
      <div class="exec-big">Your staff is drowning in coordination work that does not require human judgment — and it is costing you <span class="hl-coral">patients, revenue, and the ability to scale.</span></div>

      <div class="stat-cards">
        <div class="stat-card exec-reveal">
          <div class="stat-number">62<span class="stat-unit">%</span></div>
          <div class="stat-desc">Of staff time consumed by coordination work — routing calls, chasing referrals, updating records — that requires zero clinical judgment.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-card exec-reveal">
          <div class="stat-number">$2M<span class="stat-unit">+</span></div>
          <div class="stat-desc">Spent on undifferentiated engineering: compliance, queues, scheduling, CRM. Things every MCO needs.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-card exec-reveal">
          <div class="stat-number">37<span class="stat-unit">%</span></div>
          <div class="stat-desc">Of patient drop-off attributed to operational failures: missed calls, scheduling friction, lost follow-ups.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .exec-reality {
    padding: 80px 40px 120px;
    flex-direction: column;
    position: relative;
  }

  .reality-bg {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    z-index: 0;
  }

  .reality-bg-img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  .reality-overlay {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: rgba(10, 22, 40, 0.82);
  }

  .reality-content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .stat-cards {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 24px;
    margin-top: 20px;
  }

  .stat-card {
    background: linear-gradient(155deg, var(--navy-mid), var(--navy-light));
    border: 1px solid rgba(240,180,41,0.12);
    border-radius: 20px;
    padding: 44px 32px;
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: transform 0.3s, border-color 0.3s;
  }

  .stat-card::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 20%;
    right: 20%;
    height: 3px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--gold), var(--teal));
    border-radius: 0 0 3px 3px;
  }

  .stat-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
    border-color: rgba(240,180,41,0.25);
  }

  .stat-number {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 3.6rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--gold);
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .stat-unit {
    font-size: 2rem;
    color: var(--gold);
    opacity: 0.7;
  }

  .stat-desc {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--gray-300);
    line-height: 1.65;
    max-width: 280px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .stat-cards {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      max-width: 400px;
      margin: 20px auto 0;
    }

    .exec-reality {
      padding: 80px 24px;
    }
  }
</style>
